   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Actually these two problems the lack of building up and the lack of functioning are one thing.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>We need some to tell us why we are short of the proper building up and the proper functioning.</S>
