   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>If we are not built up or if we would not be built up, it means we are short of the growth in life.</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>If we do not function or we are unable to function, this also indicates we are short of the growth in life.</S>
   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>However, the shortage of the growth in life is due to many factors.</S>
